column4: Felt it was inaccurate  for the presenter to  describe an  interviewee’s  statement that  Facebook facilitated  illegal campaigning by  Vote Leave during the  referendum as an  “allegation”.

Felt the coverage of  claims of anti-Semitism  in the Labour Party was  biased against them  and/or the interview  with Louise Ellman  about the 2010  Holocaust event  attended by Jeremy  Corbyn was  misleading.
